      "item": "spectrum:amethyst_ore",
      "text": "Now that you are paying attention, you noticed small inclusions of gems in the rock all over the place.$(br)If you see such an ore a geode is surely not far!$(br2)While not renewable like Gemstone Clusters, Gemstone Ore provides a lot of Shards, especially when broken with a Fortune-Tool."
